高等固態物理（一）                      


  	This course is intended to provide an advanced treatment of the physics of solids for Materials Scientists. Students will be exposed to standard approximations, models and methods of condensed matter physics. The course will cover a wide variety of physical phenomena and applications of solid state materials ranging from transistors to lasers

課程教育目標 

A. 具備專業知能 
